The Ottery Boyz Motorcycle Club gathered at the Blake family home on Friday where Keith Blake and his family had prepared enough pickled fish to feed over 2000 underprivileged residents of Lansdownne, Hanover Park and Philippi.
The tradition has become an annual one, and is now in its sixth year.
– African News Agency (ANA)


